colss=list(data.columns)
colss.pop(0)
for m in colss:
    fig,axs=plt.subplots(2,2)
    count=1
    for i,j,k in zip(range(0,22,7),[[0,0],[0,1],[1,0],[1,1]],["blue","red","orange","green"]):
        count+=1
        a="tab"+":"+k
        if(count==5):
            x=datamrc["Date_tmp"][i:i+7+3]
            y=datamrc[m][i:i+7+3]
        else:
            x=datamrc["Date_tmp"][i:i+7]
            y=datamrc[m][i:i+7]
        if(count<4):
            axs[j[0], j[1]].set_title(m)
        axs[j[0],j[1]].plot(x,y,a)

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
existing_cols=list(datamr_diff.columns)
existing_cols.pop(0)
existing_cols
for i,j in zip(new_cols,existing_cols):
    datamr_diff[i]=list(range(len(datamr_diff)))
    datamr_diff[i][0]=datamr_diff[j][0]
    for k in range(0,len(datamr_diff)-1):
        datamr_diff[i][k+1]=datamr_diff[j][k+1]-datamr_diff[j][k]

    datamr_ratio[i][0]=1
    tmp=[]
    tmp.append(datamr_ratio[i][0])
    for k in range(0,len(datamr_ratio)-1):
        
        tmp.append(round(datamr_ratio[j][k+1]/datamr_ratio[j][k],2))
    datamr_ratio[i]=tmp
